- Main app logic: /public/app.js
- Styles: /public/styles.css (Tailwind build)
- HTML pages: /public/*.html
- API routes: /src/api/*.js
- Memory: /MEMORY.md
- Rules: /CLAUDE.md and /.windsurfrules
